{"tid":1637274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普︰香港示威或不利於中美經貿談判","createTime":"2019-10-08T02:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T02:42:09.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6f909c1092bdbd9c7f4b551cf0948cb7c54361","tid":1637274,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:41:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】中美周四展開新一輪高級別經貿談判，美國總統特朗普指，香港的示威可能會不利於談判。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普︰「我們希望可以看到能以非常人道方式解決，我希望這事會發生。你知香港對全球非常重要，不僅是對中國來說，對世界亦然。我只希望可以看到達致一個人道協議，我知道習主席有能力做得到，我認為他是一個令人信服的人，我們正在談判。如果發生任何不好的事，我想會對談判不利，政治上可能會很困難，可能對於我們、其他某些人以及他（習近平），但我認為他們要以和平的態度處理。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365460&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365460%26refer%3DShare&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnImipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=ec7cebd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365460%26refer%3DShare&h=5c41ce97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365460&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"63b39e7a77c2642a4889e3d0e2df1687630fa404","tid":1637274,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:42:09.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"}]}